{"tid":1440406,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「X就係鬼」只會破壞抗爭者間嘅信任 唔好再講","createTime":"2019-08-10T12:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:04:46.000Z","uid":118228,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f642ce5e165f89fd01ab8438c886885fe3b3ad86","tid":1440406,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"2014開始 雨傘革命 旺角魚蛋革命 傘後選舉 都不斷因為捉鬼而令到大家信任同撕裂越黎越大 但絕大多數最後都證明唔係鬼 請大家首先以理服人 講唔埋就道不同不相為謀 唔使話人係鬼<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話人係鬼傷害極大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n出得黎前線，大家都當大家係戰友，最慘唔係俾人拉俾人打，係明明自己人但俾人孤立<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地永遠無能力肯定一個人係咪鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔係政府，無監控無情報組織，鬼可能有，但可能捉錯十個都未捉到一個真鬼，不過已經傷害左十個抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不論前線後排鍵盤抗爭者都有唔同諗法判斷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同你嘅判斷唔一樣唔出奇，每人都有自己堅持，用自己個腦做決定，道不同不相為謀就可以<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰友一樣會做錯事 會on9</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有時會發生你覺得極on9嘅事，但好老實，on9仔周圍都有，做錯就屌佢做錯，但唔好話鬼<br />\n<br />\n5 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨放鬼最想就係令大家形住有鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n然後互不信任 猜忌 内亂 輸自己"},{"pid":"cc71e61727642fcdb7bfd272ca5c38a9fe65902e","tid":1440406,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"推！！！"},{"pid":"85cf1aa34f56d7a86a79475b856c0a52b084533e","tid":1440406,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"aa3f6d68447b995afe1b7cf3893dbdce450f3fae","tid":1440406,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:25:52.000Z","msg":"無人格的毒男 lor"},{"pid":"f1cd936df3689769b4f8f6cceaf52d2cc8f0bd07","tid":1440406,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLRgcb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLRgcb4.jpg&h=a9c36f04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1cc0dd1d186a072d9bd8c3d7b73df5f8f44bbcd","tid":1440406,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:51:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64e9ff86d88224d7d96e0c9804be06cf99bd5dea","tid":1440406,"uid":19217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:04:33.000Z","msg":"2014 輸 其中一個原因就係 捉鬼<br />\n最終變成互相猜疑"},{"pid":"4eda51856ac4f85f136870762da70fe9d248c1c5","tid":1440406,"uid":240374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"好撚on9 既事，我系任何一個tg 都會講咪撚理啲鬼<br />\n鬼系無得防，想鬧要捉鬼先系真鬼<br />\n佢地行動唔夠我地快，有鬼都唔洗理<br />\n同埋各 tg 多啲fact check 再 add group<br />\n同埋要多啲delete group 再起group<br />\n有效令到行動組既活動更安全"},{"pid":"fd98ebce8964cd061407b55e61d3c5022d98a636","tid":1440406,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:11:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5c0395020361b844d187150e589f9316dab1c60","tid":1440406,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2736b25f600a4dfd46c7cc1c5ece5805ee3bf4a3","tid":1440406,"uid":118228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"789cd26e08c8387ccd645832e875734fd7c46c3d","tid":1440406,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3406980ab5983b040d8b5a3d3a88640598bb07ab","tid":1440406,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:29:00.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"56beb0394fb654a7cbfcc47b21589c0c086cb55d","tid":1440406,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:29:15.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d3f26bea239666ba1326f4f9a846d67a15433f58","tid":1440406,"uid":299055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019